*** Please submit non packaging issue bugs to the Debian BTS and the upstream
bugzilla (https://bugzilla.samba.org/) and put a reference to the bugzilla bug
in the Debian bug report to ease bug triage for the maintainers. Thank you. ***

When applicable:
 * mention client type/OS + version
 * does the problem occur with other clients?
 * include a level 10 samba log
 * steps to reproduce the problem
 * does the problem occur with other versions of samba (oldstable, stable,
   backports, testing, ...)
